aragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3447570/extras/7321266273bc093dad0814621713b7a7.avif?t=1762586775\" width=630 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Tips:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the right mouse button to pick up and move things.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you drop something, it will break or make a sound.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If that happens, you can be caught by your mom and defeated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You win when you overcome multiple distractions and get all the food you want.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About streaming</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can upload or stream video without any restrictions.</p>",
